New:
Put the File .\AppData\Roaming\Sublime Text 3\Packages\Colorsublime - Themes\Adventure_Time.tmTheme into your user folder.






















Old:
"\AppData\Roaming\Sublime Text 3\Packages\Colorsublime - Themes\"" to change the colorSyntax.

